  <%= render :partial => 'menu' %>
  <article role="article" class="group">

    <h2>Accessibility</h2>

    <p>If you have any difficulty using the internet or have any accessibility issues, we hope the following information is useful.</p>

    <h3>I need help getting started online</h3>

    <p><a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/webwise/topics/using-the-web/">Getting started with the internet</a> <small>(BBC Web Wise)</small></p>

    <h4>Find a free course near you</h4>
    <p><a href="http://www.ukonlinecentres.com">UK Online Centres</a> offer free computer and internet training across the country. <small>(UK Online)</small></p>
    <form action="http://www.ukonlinecentres.com/centresearch/">
      <label for="findacentre">Enter a UK postcode</label>
      <input type="text" value="" id="placename" name="q"><input type="submit" value="Go" class="button">
    </form>

    <h3>I do not have regular access to an internet connection</h3>
    <p><a href="/book-internet-access-in-a-library">Book internet access in your local library</a></p>

    <h3>I find a keyboard or mouse hard to use</h3>
    <p><a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/accessibility/guides/mouse_easier/">Find out how to make your mouse easier to use</a> <small>(BBC My Web)</small></p>
    <p><a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/accessibility/guides/keyboard_mouse/">Find out how to use your keyboard to control your mouse</a> <small>(BBC My Web)</small></p>
    <p><a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/accessibility/guides/alternative_devices/">Find out about alternatives to a keyboard and mouse</a> <small>(BBC My Web)</small></p>

    <h3>I can't see very well</h3>
    <p><a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/accessibility/guides/text_larger/">Learn how to increase the size of the text in your web browser</a> <small>(BBC My Web)</small></p>
    <p><a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/accessibility/guides/change_colours/">Learn how to change text and background colours to make them easier to read</a> <small>(BBC My Web)</small></p>
    <p><a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/accessibility/guides/magnify/">Learn how to magnify your screen</a> <small>(BBC My Web)</small></p>

    <h3>I am blind</h3>
    <p><a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/accessibility/guides/screenreaders/">Find out about screen readers and talking browsers</a> <small>(BBC My Web)</small></p>

  </article>
</section>
